    "profile_summary": "**Profile**: A highly productive generalist developer with extensive experience across a wide range of technologies and domains. With over 3,600 commits contributed to more than 200 repositories, they demonstrate consistent output and a capacity to engage with diverse codebases and project requirements.\n\n**Technical Stack**:\n*   **Primary Languages**: JavaScript, TypeScript, C#, Python, PHP\n*   **Web Technologies**: HTML, Next.js\n*   **Additional Experience**: C, Visual Basic .NET, SQL, Rust, Assembly\n\n**Notable Work**: Has developed significant tooling and applications, including **FortiVault** (a security-focused project) and **SharpJolt**, a C# library for the Game Jolt API. Their portfolio also shows substantial contributions to open-source utilities, Discord bots, and full-stack web platforms.",
    "cv_section": "```markdown\n## Professional Summary\nResults-driven software engineer with proficiency in full-stack development, from low-level systems to modern web applications. Experienced in leveraging a diverse technology stack to deliver robust and scalable solutions.\n\n## Technical Skills\n*   **Languages:** TypeScript, JavaScript, C#, Python\n*   **Front-End:** HTML, TypeScript, modern JavaScript (ES6+)\n*   **Back-End:** C#, Python, PHP, Node.js\n*   **Tools & Paradigms:** Makefile, Object-Oriented Programming (OOP)\n\n## Key Projects\n*   **scrapengine:** Developed a high-performance web scraping engine using TypeScript for efficient data extraction and processing.\n*   **vox:** Engineered a cross-platform command-line utility with a custom Makefile build system for streamlined project automation.\n*   **LyeZinho:** Created a feature-rich Discord bot to automate community management tasks and enhance user engagement.\n```",
